        <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="123,30,0,0" TextWrapping="Wrap" Text="TicTacToe is a game where the objective is to string together three &quot;X&quot; or three &quot;O&quot; in a row. You can win in three ways, which is to match up the three &quot;X&quot; or &quot;O&quot; vertically, horizontally, or diagonally. To play, you must click in the unopen space within the game board to place an &quot;X&quot; or &quot;O&quot;. " VerticalAlignment="Top" Height="90" Width="564" FontFamily="Arial" FontSize="16"/>
